Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three more minutes! \NThey'll be there in three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in Ueno, sir. {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Floor it! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please die for real this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Akino, the designer in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, the cups of this bra are made entirely of tulle lace, providing a flexible and fast fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The main selling point \Nis this boldly-placed zipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Akino-kun, we find that idea interesting, but doesn't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? Hurt... how?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When you close it, does anything ever get caught in the zipper? {nc what's hiyaga, was inmo/pubic hair in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wore it all day myself, \Nand that didn’t happen even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! You wear it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. We approve it as Pretty's \Nnew product line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was very impressive. \NNext is Kondo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would look at these shorts I designed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's my turn to present. \NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it, come on! \NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the diaper shorts I designed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Practical shorts with excellent liquid absorption...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:14.08,Overlap,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if your underwear gets soiled by discharge, \Nwhich is common among women,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you won’t have to worry with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Kondo-kun, I think we've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking with that diaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our company makes women's underwear, \Nnot baby products!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really the design for the once-a-month prototype presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone worked on for two days straight without going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The result was the same as if you hadn't come to work for two days straight! {no clue what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you ever so much for embarrassing me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Pretty Design Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Kondo? Who's asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kondo is away right now. {unsure: いま彼は席をはずしていますがはい}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's been absent since yesterday. {same, also unsure why he'd say that}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Personal calls on the company phone are not allowed, you know! {勤務中に私用の電話は困るね!さっさと仕事をしたまえ!!!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to your desk and do something good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a little unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Akino-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Focusing on diaper shorts for women is an interesting perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but they can’t be worn under tight skirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Director, it's almost time for our commercial to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding last night’s attack on the leader of the Shinsen Family, the police
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,have announced that they will work with with the Osakan and Metropolitan Police Departments,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,since the evidence suggests that the perpetrators belong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Kansai-based Choshu Group, \Nwho may be part of a larger conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinsen Family President Kondo Isamiashi is currently
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in the police hospital under intensive care. {/in critical condition}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,600)}In other news...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of our way, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us in, goddammit! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Young boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry! We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was by his side all the time, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So my father is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, Shizuya came to check on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He died mere moments ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I called...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I called you time and time again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Namakura, what's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Hijikata, {\i1}counting on ya to cover my back!{\i0} {assuming he means "please follow me" meaning I'll assume the group leadership now and be ahead of you}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid? You're at a funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. They're already fighting \Nfor the front row seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,These two underbosses are the most powerful figures in the family, {probably https://jisho.org/word/%E8%B2%B8%E3%81%97%E5%85%83 but that seems too specific}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,now vying for the position of successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Successor? I thought Shizuya-san was the heir apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The young boss is not cut out to be yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the madam is still trying to convince him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So quiet... {implied [you are], shizuya misunderstands as [in here]}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even hear the sutras here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that you are being very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father was murdered, \Nyet you are unfazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, all the hotheads of the family could only imagine Kingoro Choshu in that coffin. {unsure why she says "put the choshu family signboard; sign; billboard in the coffin"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a mere bystander, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but being in the underworld... \NIt's like you're stuck in a perpetual car crash. {/gangster society}{unsure what he means: 極道社会じゃ交通事故にあったようなもんでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuya, from today onwards, \Nyou are the third president of the Shinsen Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hijikata and Namakura are about to clash fiercely for the right to succeed our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you do it instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,there won't be bloodshed. {/it's the best for everyone}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But mom, I already have a proper job...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this is a job worthy of a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My prototype...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The rejected breastfeeding bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ridicule me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll lead a double life as both an office worker and the president of the Shinsen Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll become the Quiet Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kondo, is that you? \NWalking here all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes... I felt that I would endanger others by walking with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's dangerous 'bout that, huh? \NAfraid they might trip over you? {nc what he means: でかい屈でも、こくのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, mister! We are offering a special service to commemorate our opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All-you-can-drink for just 1,000 yen and an extra bottle to take home! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And right now all our girls happen to be free! {not sure what he means by "all are in luck"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not messing with me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 1,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's carry on here! {二軒目}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Chief, but I'm abstaining, so you'll have to go without me. {non-drinker; someone who cannot drink​}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? \NWe just met and you wanna leave us already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, come on in, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still tag along, Kondo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll order some oolong tea for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Four customers—go welcome them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Boop! Oops, I did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to stop! \NWe're not {\i1}that{\i0} kind of establishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you ought to start doing that starting tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At least once its dark, come on, babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you, Kondo? \NDrinking nothing but oolong tea tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of our company, \Nwhich sells women's panties and bras, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not in my life, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you take that last week off for, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was for business...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Chief, how Kondo chooses to use his paid leave is none of your business, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Akino-chan, there's no need to get so defensive, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're secretly into Kondo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ah, I'm such a lonely woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Comfort me already!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaoka, we need another \Nround of refreshments! {/hors d'oeuvres ; unsure, not in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, please stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving him straight whiskey when he's abstaining is reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What harm will a single cup do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondo-kun, you don't need to push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I'll drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bottoms up! Bottoms up! \NBottoms up! Bottoms up! Bottoms up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We hereby recognize Kondo Shizuya
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as the third president of the Shinsen Family, the legal heir of the previous president.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please drink it when your mind is made up. {unsure what he means by 腹定まったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the ceremonial sake permeate through your soul. {no clue what he means/says, not in manga: hide the cup deep in your pocket}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, congratulations are in order!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This marks the official birth \Nof our third president!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it together, Namakura! \NAt least during a solemn ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we be celebrating the birth \Nof the third president?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're dissatisfied with this choice of successor, huh, Hijikata? My, oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you're unhappy that Shizuya-san, the son of our beloved second president, took over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve to say that in front of the many bosses who came from all over the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I ever say such nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a wonderful third president we got!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,With him, the future of the Shinsen Family is secured!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see those two, Shizuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Hijikata and Namakura were after the president's seat themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They lost sleep over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they keep their word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I quite enjoy my current "honest" life. {/of an honest/non-yakuza person}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only to prevent those two from escalating it into an open conflict {very unsure, not in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've become the third president.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You should do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A position of power \Nor a cheap office worker's position—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll quickly find out \Nwhich one is more comfortable for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, it turns out you know how to drink, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stop, Kondo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's good! Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He finished the bottle in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn’t look the slightest bit tipsy! {lit: face color didn't change at all}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he secretly be the biggest drinker known to man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. You're no fun. I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for the visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure thing! I'll come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... \NTwo... 279,000 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?! Why does it cost so much for one bottle and some snacks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ni-Nigeno-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In these parts, it is customary to pay the bill for what you’ve eaten and drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, you twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay up, wontcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure... But you see, that price is a bit steep for me right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me deal with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I ended up \Ndrinking most of it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, really? W-Well, if you say so. \NWe'll leave you to it, then! Let's go now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Can Kondo-kun really pay for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go already! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So you’re the walking treasury \Nfor those dolts? {/finance minister}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have a couple of 100 yen coins on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya lookin' down on us? \NLookin' down, aintcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I intend to pay you with labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to help you with this scam. {(intentional) overcharging; rip-off; highway robbery}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, show this twit our menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They all look painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll call your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have your family bring the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You phone number—say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, is this the Kondo family house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have your son here, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought it was a good idea to pig out at our restaurant without having any money on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll be there in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming already. \NUntil then, you stay here and behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we shouldn't have called them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where do you think you're going? \NKnow your fucking place! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never catch up with me! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinsen Family assault force leader Inokubi Koshiro is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone. I'd like you all to help this place with their scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye! Roger that, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:17:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,President, why did you allow that scum \Nto treat you like trash? {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd never lay a finger on you if you told them you were our President. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just not my preferred way to do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they're just some scam artists?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, we should've at least compensated them for that bottle I drank... {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,President, Boss Hijikata is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hijikata?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be \Nthis late at night, Hijikata?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's the only time \Nwhen you're available, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We held a conference with the other underbosses today, and there's something we need to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going to exact revenge for your late father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Choshu bastards are mocking our group in broad daylight at every occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is outrageous! We're being made into a laughing stock for all the other organizations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If they want to laugh, then let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In the underworld, we can't just brush it off like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shinsen Family is in crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hijikata, are you trying to order me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It is no order, it's a plea, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NYou're not usually like that, Hijikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have time to make women’s panties,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn’t you spare a bit of it \Nto think about this organization's future?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? So you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Namakura told me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after becoming president, \Nyou refused to quit your honest job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How come the president of the Shinsen Family works for a panty-making company by day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes me feel so miserable... \NSo miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In any organization, \Nthe word of the higher-ups is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t tolerate you lecturing me ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Night is a dangerous time. \NYou should go home. {夜はなにかとぶっそうだはやく帰んなさい in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you that hellbent on keeping your honest job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of living entirely in the yakuza world. {自分が極道の世界に身をおくことがね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of being so timid if you're already the president?! {総長たるもんがそんな臆病でどうしますんや!!!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You must prove yourself! {lit: it's about capacity/abilities}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't demonstrate that you have what it takes to be a leader, the people won't follow you! {ko = children = everyone else in the organization}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go places in the yakuza world \Nwith your parent's reputation alone! {benefiting from the influence of a master or parent}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hijikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, did you hear what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What he truly meant was that he’s afraid of himself in this world. {unsure what she means}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid of himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hijikata, you probably think I’m a fool for elevating Shizuya to this position just because he’s my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps you think that I did it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,simply to prevent a succession war between you and Namakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuya is a yakuza by nature. {/born}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s afraid of awakening the blood of a ferocious yakuza that lies dormant within him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he clings onto his honest job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,His father always said that only Shizuya could succeed him as the third president.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw through Shizuya's makings of a yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he's a placid man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s because you don’t know what he’s truly like when you really stir him up. {/when he gets really angry}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit for brains!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,These Kishu Family assholes said they can't send reinforcements! {鬼州組は応援部隊を送れんといってきおった!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what we've settled on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck did we even get the Shinsen president out of the way for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If all-out war broke out between Kishu and Shinsen, the cops would take down both of them! {鬼州組と新鮮組が全面戦争になれば警察にどちらもつぶされるなどとぬかしやがって!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.95,0:22:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that our plan from the get-go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If he meant it, then why are we the only ones risking our necks now? {no clue what's tamanerawashi here, not in manga; could be "If it was true, then why is there a hunting season on us now?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They even sent their best hitman after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we to wage this war against the Shinsen Family on our own?! {わしらだけであの新鮮組と戦えちゅうんかい}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a moron, Setsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, if it came to this, \Nwe have no choice but to prepare for the worst. {こうなったら腹くくるしかないでしょう - literally "wrap/tie around the belly"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been prepared for ages! {lit: long ago wrapped - refers to the ropes}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this, I have all fronts covered! {lit: I even wrapped my ass}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know when and where the Shinsen hitman will attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt anyone is going to make an attempt at your hindquarters. {lit: dig your ass - means exactly what you think it means}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.57,0:22:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know if their hitman is not some faggot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,who likes to do \Nhis victims from behind?! {オカマ掘りながら脳天ぶちぬくのが好きなヒットマンがいるかもしれんじゃないか!!! - lit: okama who shoots through to the top of the head - not sure what he means, maybe that the okama would shoot him while he rapes him, figuratively shooting him through from the asshole to the top of the head}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to calm down, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the Shinsen Family has been eerily quiet lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.43,0:22:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Their ranks include over 260 groups, \N10,000 members total.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In turn, our group numbers less than 100 members, even if we include the small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say? {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Tamaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.38,0:23:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that the killer might come from our own men, the Kishu Family? {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me that you won't let him get away with it! {same}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.42,0:23:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.48,0:23:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Great news, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy overheard at a gambling den {no clue waht's shireta}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that the Shinsen Family’s new Prez, \Nsomeone named Shizuya, is a cretin, sir! A cretin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A cretin?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, even after getting appointed as the president, he kept his honest job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so he ain't a yakuza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.02,0:23:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Hijikata and Namakura \Nare also paralyzed by his inaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shinsen Family \Nis falling apart at the seams!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we can still win this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting is not about numbers, \Nit's about courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It all hinges on one's leader's qualities. {/what kind of leader he is}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If their third Prez is such a pushover, \Nwe have this in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said, Tamaki! \NWar is not a matter of numbers only.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have a leader who's a real man, \Nwe can do just fine without help from Kishu! {lit: thanks to Choshu Kingoro (himself) being manly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll haunt and terrify him, and when he's scared shitless, I'll deal the final blow myself... {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it'll be! {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.68,0:24:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondo-kun, I'm sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn’t have left you all alone at a shady place like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.73,0:24:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, why should I be mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what do you think about this design? Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you have zero sense of style. {maybe "it's senseless"}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.03,0:24:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Kondo. \NWhat does your family do for a living
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,where you can afford to pay 300,000 to a sham business?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.03,0:24:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Well, our income is a bit above average. {/more or less rich}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.80,0:24:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you dawdling \Nwhen your boss is waiting for a light?! {lit: don't you pay attention when your superior is chewing a cigarette}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.10,0:24:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.28,0:24:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay attention, you dimwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.18,0:24:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Kondo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.03,0:24:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.07,0:24:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't mention to the Chief \Nthat you're rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.92,0:24:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s terribly resentful of the rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.74,0:24:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's a proletarian at heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.12,0:25:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait any longer! \NI'll do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.12,0:25:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In a week, the Choshu Group \Nwill be wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.55,0:25:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My Namakura Group would handle it much more deftly!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.82,0:25:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we're the strongest battle formation in the Shinsen Family. {was 'After all, we're the strongest combat formation in the Shinsen Family.'}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.87,0:25:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Namakura, how can your merry band \Nbe considered a battle formation? {武闘派 / budouha = combatants/military force, was 'Namakura, how can your merry band \Nbe considered a combat formation?'}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.13,0:25:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, did you mean to say "ballet formation?" {日本舞踊派 / buyouha = Japanese dance school, was 'Oh, sorry, did you mean to say "compact formation?" '}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.36,0:25:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, you chrome dome?! {tsurutenpika - refers to https://nishinomiya-style.jp/glossary/turuten ; it seems he's making a comment on Hijikata's baldness, comparing his head to spheres polished by tourists rubbing them}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.88,0:25:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrome dome? We'll see how bald you'll be when you're my age! {no clue waht he means: 古いハゲのいい方しやがって}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.88,0:25:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop this nonsense, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.36,0:25:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The president will probably tell us \Nto stay away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.40,0:25:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okita! Where the hell have you ever seen a yakuza who lets his parent's murderers go unpunished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.39,0:25:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.00,0:25:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure the president is acting on his own endgame plan. {lit: has deep thoughts about it}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.87,0:25:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Choshu Group from Chiba \Nis backed by the Kishu Family from the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.83,0:25:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The president won't be so rash as to attack them head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.20,0:25:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The president is still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.44,0:25:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we must rally him more actively!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.84,0:26:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the yelling about, Hijikata?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.18,0:26:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.37,0:26:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.12,0:26:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow my group \Nto avenge your late father!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.30,0:26:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't I told you already \Nthat we can't do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.60,0:26:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't know when to give up, Hijikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.40,0:26:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,President! Do you intend to leave your parent’s murder unpunished? To let them get away with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.90,0:26:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it only natural for children to avenge their parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.14,0:26:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You all keep calling him my parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.04,0:26:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me, it was my own \Nfather who got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.07,0:26:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand the feelings I'm having to suppress.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.22,0:26:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Unauthorized actions \Nwill put everyone in a fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.30,0:26:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my lunch break is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.81,0:26:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us put a full stop to it here. \NKeep up the good work. {/let's not bring it up again}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.98,0:26:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in times like these, \Nhe prioritizes making panties over the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.78,0:26:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You should watch your mouth, Hijikata. {/choose your words more carefully}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.67,0:27:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If it came to this, we have no choice but to ask Uncle Okubo for help. {not literal uncle ofc, rather "someone seen as a patron"}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.87,0:27:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.64,0:27:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone! \NEverything in order? {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.87,0:27:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, if it isn't Matsudaira-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.00,0:27:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So nice of you to visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.29,0:27:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just dropping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.00,0:27:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.69,0:27:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, kid. {/go somewhere else}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.88,0:27:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.51,0:27:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Working hard, Akino-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.20,0:27:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I like that design!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.43,0:27:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you wearing \Nsomething similar yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.92,0:27:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about we take a breather \Nand go get some coffee together?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.30,0:27:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.45,0:27:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, does she have any urgent work? {/special assignment}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.40,0:27:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! Actually, Akino is supposed to be on break right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.71,0:27:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! It's settled, then. \NCome on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.78,0:27:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I really can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.98,0:27:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can. \NCome on, let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.70,0:27:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager, where should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.83,0:27:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole! You did that on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.16,0:27:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.44,0:27:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,B-By no means, Matsudaira-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.12,0:27:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn’t have the brains or the guts \Nto do that on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.92,0:28:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you apologizing yet, Kondo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.87,0:28:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.14,0:28:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, it popped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.85,0:28:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For god's sake, \Nwhat were you three thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.09,0:28:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,President, do you really want our company to stop dealing in Pretty's products?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.87,0:28:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I do hear people saying that underwear from European brands happens to be sturdier.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.74,0:28:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s not allow this incident \Nto leave a sour taste in our mouths. {, Matsudaira-sama}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.92,0:28:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize, Kondo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.95,0:28:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.48,0:28:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.32,0:28:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see your tie is crooked?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.09,0:28:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.82,0:28:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.83,0:28:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.11,0:28:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For the small fry like you, I can terminate your employment whenever I feel like it! {low-ranking employee ... can make your head roll anytime = figuratively means "to fire"; later there's a reverse joke at 31:18, hence weird wording}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.79,0:28:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how about dinner with me tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.60,0:28:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.05,0:28:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Akino-kun, why don't you and the manager \Nentertain Matsudaira-san tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.44,0:28:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.80,0:29:00.06,Overlap,,0,0,0,,President, I don't want the baldy. {/will get in the way - he pretty much says it directly now, without beating round the bush}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.06,0:29:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.18,0:29:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kido-kun, you stay! {no clue what's his name, on wiki it only lists his surname}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.50,0:29:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Akino-chan is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.11,0:29:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do? \NHe's the top brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.66,0:29:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, what a pity—{\i1}he{\i0} is the only son of Matsudaira Genta of the Toto Distribution Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.52,0:29:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.62,0:29:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Toto Department Store weren’t our primary wholesale retailer, I’d have torn him to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.30,0:29:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager, you seem quite salty about being left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.01,0:29:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a big shot, all right... {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.96,0:29:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't restrain yourself, Akino-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.70,0:29:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.80,0:29:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're happy to see you here tonight, Matsudaira-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.72,0:29:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You! What the hell happened today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.49,0:29:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that whenever I come, #1, Teresa, through #3, Kei, should already be here! {including #2}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.37,0:29:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.98,0:29:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Number three, Kei, is so in love with me, \Nshe always suddenly starts smooching me! {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.23,0:30:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Matsudaira-sama, \Nunfortunately, all three are occupied for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.15,0:30:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you saying there's a customer more important than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.67,0:30:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.67,0:30:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! You prick!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.63,0:30:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.63,0:30:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,These three women \Nare always reserved for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.60,0:30:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm taking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.64,0:30:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.99,0:30:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.56,0:30:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm from the Toto Group, the national monopolist! { supremacy over a nation}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.46,0:30:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think you can butt in and demand someone for yourself, huh? {not a word}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.64,0:30:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.76,0:30:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.53,0:30:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is important to our company.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.73,0:30:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.87,0:30:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See if I give a fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.51,0:30:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokubi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.89,0:31:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't refuse the honest-working lady's request. Forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.55,0:31:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.05,0:31:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we must've scared you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.57,0:31:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Your tie is all crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.32,0:31:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Appreciate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.10,0:31:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you shouldn't push your luck \Nwhen having fun with girls. {女遊びで図に乗ら\Nんほうがいい\Nその気になれば、いつだってあなたの首を飛ばせるんですから･･････\N胴体から - says "boku-chan" to diminish himself, not sure why}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.72,0:31:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can terminate your employment \Nwhenever I feel like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.67,0:31:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with your life. {lit: I can make your head roll... away from your torso = not figuratively, behead him; I also considered for this and the original line "I can send you back to Classyfields... in a coffin" or "back to newspapers... as an obituary" or "send back home, jobless / in a coffin" or "scratch you off the company payroll / from among the living"}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.98,0:31:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.69,0:31:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.61,0:31:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.75,0:31:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.22,0:31:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.54,0:31:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.56,0:31:47.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,I can terminate your life whenever I feel like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.90,0:31:49.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,Terminate...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.39,0:31:55.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,Where... Where have I heard that line before?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.11,0:32:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, sir!{gokuro}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.95,0:32:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Okubo, we welcome you. {a Yakuza AND a kansai-ben one... feels like I've won a lottery but I wish I didn't}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.51,0:32:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Namakura and Hijikata,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.72,0:32:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,if the third president really is as worthless as you make him out to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.69,0:32:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him! {斬る！}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.60,0:32:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember becoming the guardian of an idiot! {後見人}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.52,0:32:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gotta be careful with him...{/dangerous grandpa}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.39,0:32:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, I never thought \NI'd drink with you like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.27,0:32:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have to sever \Nyour own son from you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.58,0:32:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.25,0:33:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, President? \NI called for you a while ago. {unsure, maybe "you called me first"}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.60,0:33:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With a sword cane? {swordstick; sword cane; loaded cane}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.76,0:33:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Boss Okumo really go to meet Shizuya \Nwith a hidden blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.53,0:33:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He said if he doesn't find the new president capable enough, he'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.52,0:33:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, are you sure \Nthe third president will make it through?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.90,0:33:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.77,0:33:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I'm worried about is Boss Okubo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.40,0:33:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.25,0:33:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.64,0:33:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I’m sure you have some plans regarding the Choshu Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.96,0:33:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. I never thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.16,0:33:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't they do away with your pops?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.42,0:33:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep letting people make fun of you, \NI won't be able to remain the family's guardian! {lit: I don't remember becoming the guardian of the laughing stock}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.58,0:33:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I never really asked you to be one \Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.51,0:33:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you're really trying my patience here! {わしも気が長くなったもんよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.03,0:33:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, anyone who talked to me like that \Nwould be dead by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.95,0:34:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I'm busy today. \NCould you come another time? {/go home}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.15,0:34:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is inventory day, \Nand I'm going to be late because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.65,0:34:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard! So you really are still working at your honest job!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.91,0:34:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It seems someone told you already?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.16,0:34:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Then it's true that it's for a company \Nmaking women's panties...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.17,0:34:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Actually, you have a daughter about my age back home, don't you? {actually toshigoro probably means "adult" but not "old" so like "target audience age for our panties"}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.06,0:34:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I could give you a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.46,0:34:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.14,0:34:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If he flashes his sword in front of Shizuya...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.40,0:34:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.65,0:34:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all here?\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.38,0:34:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle seems to have had a bit too much. {/a little drunk}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.78,0:34:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.44,0:34:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.63,0:35:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.16,0:35:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yessir...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.47,0:35:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I fucking told you to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.98,0:35:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.25,0:35:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tae-san, I've got quite a lot of questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.68,0:35:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's about Shizuya, \Nit might take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.98,0:35:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Manager? I got the fabric. \NI also secured the silk delivery. {no clue what's hooru / fooru here, could only find a fabric called "morris fall" but that seems irrelevant}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.43,0:35:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. Maybe you're better suited for sales than design.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.15,0:35:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just go home \Nwithout stopping by today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.68,0:35:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But there's a design meeting in the afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.41,0:35:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll go more smoothly without you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.73,0:35:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.02,0:35:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bull's eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.63,0:36:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Tamaki? \NCan this guy really be their president?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.78,0:36:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.70,0:36:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, we can do it \Nwithout relying on Kishu.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.37,0:36:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, the Shinsen Family is here... {yatsu ga kimashita = guy / guys have arrived - he means one guy and Choshu thinks it's the entire family}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.61,0:36:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Imbecile! What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.25,0:36:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet them guns blazing! {lit: bring out the irons}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.61,0:36:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just one guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.81,0:36:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.26,0:36:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.13,0:36:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.98,0:36:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, it's is Shizuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.24,0:36:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.14,0:36:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, did you come here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.58,0:36:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what kinda place this is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.02,0:36:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.01,0:36:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I happened to in the vicinity for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.57,0:36:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I might drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.04,0:36:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there’s a favor \NI’d like to ask of Choshu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.89,0:36:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.99,0:36:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They broke off from the Kishu Family? {no clue whats teihiitori here, this is where the show goes separate ways with manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.41,0:36:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.08,0:36:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.39,0:36:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather everyone, arm yourselves! {no clue what's kabamodane, but I sense somthing about knives}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.39,0:37:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll crush Choshu once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.89,0:37:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.65,0:37:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please dissolve your organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.24,0:37:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You do that, and we’ll both forget the past wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.96,0:37:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? \NThat'd be hella apropos!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.63,0:37:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,President, that's unconditional surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.46,0:37:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But in our position, \Nwe actually have some leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.46,0:37:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, their most valuable piece has fallen straight into our hands. {gyoku = king chess piece - I really dunno what other analogy could work here}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.18,0:37:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.78,0:37:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, the amateur! How can we ever accept such conditions, you cretin? {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.14,0:37:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take this seriously. My men will grumble again if I return empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.08,0:37:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s wrap this up quickly and go home. \NAt this rate, I’ll be late for work tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.21,0:37:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's manifesting disrespect. {/looking down on us}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.66,0:37:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you! Want us to slaughter you here and now, like we did with your daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.34,0:37:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were coming, so I was waiting fully prepared! Wanna check for yourself? {lit: I also have the bell and ass wrapped - you already know why}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.27,0:37:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, it's okay. \NNo need to show it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.81,0:37:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.76,0:38:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.36,0:38:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please disband.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.87,0:38:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.25,0:38:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,S-See it, people?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.44,0:38:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The president of the Shinsen Family \Nkneels down before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.28,0:38:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How'd you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.61,0:38:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.89,0:38:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be the Namakura Group who arrives there first and puts Hijikata to shame! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.58,0:38:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be the ones who takes Choshu's head! \NYou got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.06,0:38:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.60,0:38:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.08,0:38:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think things will go as you want if you just kneel down?! {土下座したぐれえで事が思うようにはこぶと\N思っとるんか!!!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.79,0:38:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want us to disband that badly, \Nyou'll have to crawl under my groin! {/pass between my legs - need something offensive enough}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.62,0:38:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokubi, did you let the president know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.81,0:38:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He never showed up in his office. \NI thought it was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.75,0:38:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry! \NThe Namakura Group is heading there too! {no clue what's akimasen}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.79,0:38:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They left already?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.82,0:39:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a fool, Okita! {"no good/must not" - means "your methods of asking boss for permission to attack won't do"}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.42,0:39:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than waiting for the president's permission, we'll do it under Uncle Okubo's orders! {very unsure what he means but it's again something about "with or without president's permission, uncle ordered us to do it"}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.82,0:39:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We must get there, whatever it takes! \NPrepare for some action, everyone! {no clue what he means by "don't lose your fingers"}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.14,0:39:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He really crawled through it! \NDid you see that, Tamaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.06,0:39:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what power allows you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.56,0:39:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! Yeah.\NThe powerful rule the world. {no clue what he means by "don't stop at strength"}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.52,0:39:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! If you want us to disband, you're gonna have to lick my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.75,0:39:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? If you lick them, we'll disband. \NYou want it or not, fucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.10,0:39:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For real this time? {/are you telling the truth}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.46,0:39:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shinsen Family is on the move? {this is kishu, I assume}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.42,0:39:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we just received a call from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.11,0:39:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How many troops are they going to use? \NHow do they plan to deal with Choshu? {lit: get choshu's head - literally}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.60,0:39:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Find out and report back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.42,0:39:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir! Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.00,0:40:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it! \NDid you see that, you slackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.80,0:40:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He licked my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.19,0:40:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This means you'll disband from today on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.23,0:40:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.89,0:40:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is this dunce talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.07,0:40:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid? Who'd disband a group \Nover something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.53,0:40:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you lied to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.77,0:40:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.16,0:40:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you lick my heels next! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.76,0:40:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.55,0:40:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.97,0:40:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.85,0:40:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a dead man! {no clue here and for the rest of the fight}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.91,0:40:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.90,0:40:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.78,0:41:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see Namakura's frustrated face.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.54,0:41:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are the cops after us \Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.05,0:41:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! We'll split into two groups!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.29,0:41:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever shakes them off first \Ngets to kill Choshu!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.73,0:41:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.15,0:41:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Huh? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.74,0:41:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! The Shinsen president!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.10,0:41:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.81,0:41:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.00,0:41:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll disband! We'll disband, you hear?! \NWe'll disband! Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.13,0:42:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, we're late after all? \NMotherfuckers...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.36,0:42:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hijikata, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.97,0:42:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You were fucking lucky this time! {no clue what he means by "freely; impudently; brazenly; shamelessly; however one wishes"}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.38,0:42:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.05,0:42:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.86,0:42:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.66,0:42:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.47,0:42:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was wrong. {meaning "I thought you were that yakuza I saw but I was wrong"}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.53,0:42:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.56,0:42:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Akino-chan met a cool-as-a-cucumber yakuza the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.04,0:42:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a wonderful person!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.81,0:42:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, he was about your height \Nand had a square face just like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.28,0:43:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be some very important boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.70,0:43:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If their boss really looked like that,  \Nthat organization would fall apart in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.56,0:43:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My face is not that bad? {unsure, maybe "why do you think so" or "it's not that bad"}
